ImagePath +:/usr/X11R6/include/X11/pixmaps/:/usr/X11R6/include/X11/bitmaps/
ImagePath +:/usr/include/X11/bitmaps/
Read /etc/X11/fvwm/menudefs.hook Quiet
Read menudefs.hook Quiet

